"Welcome to the Kelp Research Station! Site B is looking pretty bad. We need you to investigate the cause."
"Urban here. Looking for help in figuring out why the kelp are more healthy at Site A."
"Looking for someone to investigate whether or not Site B can be fixed."
"Need someone to verify if a new kelp refuge can be constructed."
"The urchin barren had Urchins and Giant Kelp. Simulate how these populations will change over time."
"Prediciton successful. The simulator shows that the urchin barren at Site B is only going to get worse."
"Can an urchin barren be repaired? Use what you've learned from healthy Kelp Forests to intervene with the Urchin Baren
"Intervention successful. The simulator shows that the urchin barren can be repaired by releasing sea otters."
"Is an urchin barren likely to occur in the cool kelp forest?"
"Prediction successful. Ecosystem is sustainable for the forseeable future."
"How does Sargassum change the light levels and affect the Staghorn Coral?"
"Prediciton successful. The simulator shows Sargassum reduces the light to levels dangerous to Staghorn Coral."
"How does the number of Fishers affect the Red Grouper population?"
"Prediciton successful. The simulator shows up to 40 Fishers can safely sustain the Red Grouper population."
